      Output: 🔒 RIGOR LEVEL: FULL · 📋 REASON: code-impl in BFF (.cs DI module modification, tag bff-api, ADR-010 + bff-extensions §F.1 directly applicable) — quality gates Step 9.5 required · Proceeding with Step 0...
